          "label": "Headings & products",
          "info": "One item per line. Heading line: start with ## (e.g. ## Sneaker Care Kits). Product line: Label | handle (handle = the product or collection handle). Optional extra fields: Label | handle | search terms | small caption. Add a line to add a product; delete a line to remove it."
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "max_blocks": 20
}
